description: Go Green Network is an active Eco-club within Cornell that unites students to fight against Climate Change in their local communities. We believe in the philosophy : Think Global, Act Local . We actively organize student-led movements to raise awareness about environmental issues inside and outside our campus. Our goal is to fight climate change along with millions of other students in the world
